<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Home</title>
    <link
      rel="icon"
      type="image/x-icon"
      href="https://dumbways.id/favicon.ico"
    />
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto&family=Roboto+Condensed&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://site-assets.fontawesome.com/releases/v6.4.2/css/all.css"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/universal.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
          <!-- Nabvar -->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-nav-color py-3 sticky-top">
      <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand me-4" href="/">
          <img src="/img/logo.png" alt="logo" />
        </a>
        <button
          class="navbar-toggler"
          type="button"
          data-bs-toggle="collapse"
          data-bs-target="#navbarSupportedContent"
          aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-label="Toggle navigation"
        >
          <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
          <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0 h5">
            <li class="nav-item me-4">
              <a
                class="nav-link active text-dark"
                aria-current="page"
                href="/"
              >Home</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item me-4">
              <a class="nav-link text-dark" href="/project/add-project">Add Project</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link text-dark" href="/testimonial">Testimonials</a>
            {{#if data.isNotAuthorized}}
             <li class="nav-item me-4">
              <a class="nav-link text-dark" href="/auth/login">Login</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item me-4">
              <a class="nav-link text-dark" href="/auth/register">Register</a>
            </li>
            {{/if}}
             <li class="nav-item me-4">
              <a href="#">{{data.duration}}</a> 
            </li>
       

            
          </ul>
          <a class="btn btn-dark hover-white me-4" href="/auth/logout">Logout</a>
          <a
            class="btn btn-dark hover-white"
            type="submit"
            href="/contact-me"
          >Contact Me</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <!-- End Navbar -->
    <!-- Card Content -->
   <div class="bg-body-secondary overflow-hidden">
      <div class="container my-5">
        <div class="card shadow-lg mb-5 bg-body-tertiary rounded">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
              <!--penggunaan grid-->
              <div class="col-md-6 ps-5 py-5">
                <h1>My Profile</h1>
                <p class="fs-5" style="text-align: justify">
                  Nama saya Sultan Bransyah, saya biasa dipanggil tan. Saya
                  berasal dari Kota Banda Aceh. Saya merupakan alumni program
                  studi Teknik Komputer di salah satu universitas yang ada di
                  Kota Banda Aceh yang bernama Universitas Syiah Kuala. <br />
                  Kegiatan saya sebelum mengikuti bootcamp ini adalah mengikuti
                  beberapa kelas online seperti dicoding dan mencari beberapa
                  lowongan pekerjaan untuk fresh graduate. Bahasa pemrograman
                  yang saya pelajari selama kuliah adalah Python, namun dalam
                  pengerjaan skripsi saya menggunakan Dart dikarenakan saya
                  membuat sebuah aplikasi berbasis android yang dapat mengontrol
                  sebuah alat yang dirancang menggunakan arduino.
                </p>
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mt-3">
                  <button class="btn btn-dark me-3 rounded-pill">
                    Contact
                  </button>
                  <button class="btn btn-dark rounded-pill">
                    Download CV <i class="fa-solid fa-download"></i>
                  </button>
                </div>
                <div
                  class="social-media d-flex align-items-center mt-3 fs-1"
                  style="cursor: pointer"
                >
                  <a href="#"
                    ><i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin text-dark me-3"></i
                  ></a>
                  <a href="#"
                    ><i class="fa-brands fa-square-instagram text-dark me-3"></i
                  ></a>
                  <a href="#"
                    ><i class="fa-brands fa-facebook text-dark me-3"></i
                  ></a>
                  <a href="#"
                    ><i class="fa-brands fa-square-twitter text-dark"></i
                  ></a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6 ps-5 py-5">
                <div
                  class="card shadow-lg mb-5 bg-body-tertiary rounded w-75 rounded"
                  style="width: 18rem"
                >
                  <img
                    src="/img/profilPhoto.jpg"
                    class="card-img-top"
                    alt="Photo Profile"
                  />
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="text-center fw-bold">Sultan Bransyah</h5>
                    <p class="text-center">Fullstack Developer</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- End Card Content -->

    <!-- My Project -->
    <div class="bg-white overflow-hidden">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="text-center my-5">My Project</h1>
        <div class="row gap-4 d-flex">
          {{#each data}}
            <div class="card shadow rounded" style="width: 25rem">
              <a href="/project/detail-project/{{this.id}}" class="text-decoration-none text-black">
                <div style="height: 270px" class="overflow-hidden" > 
                  <img src="{{this.img}}" class="card-img-top" alt="Profile Sultan" />
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title fw-bold">{{this.projectName}}</h5>
                  <p class="card-text">duration: {{this.duration}} Month</p>
                  <p class="card-text">author: {{this.authorName}}</p>
                  <p class="card-text" style="text-align: justify">
                    {{this.description}}
                  </p>
              </a>
                <div class="d-flex gap-4 my-4" id="logo_tech" style="font-size: 1.5rem;">
                  {{#if this.nodeJs}}
                   <i class="fab fa-node fa"></i>
                  {{/if}}
                  {{#if this.nextJs}}
                  <i class="fa-brands fa-android"></i>
                  {{/if}}
                    {{#if this.reactJs}}
                   <i class="fa-brands fa-react"></i>
                  {{/if}}
                    {{#if this.typeScript}}
                   <i class="fa-brands fa-algolia"></i>
                  {{/if}}
                </div>

                <div class="d-flex gap-4 my-4">
                  <a
                    class="btn btn-dark hover-white w-50 rounded-pill"
                    href="project/update/{{this.id}}"
                    role="button"
                  >Edit</a>

                  <a
                   
                    class="btn btn-dark hover-white w-50 rounded-pill"
                    href="project/delete/{{this.id}}"
                    role="button"
                  >Delete</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          {{/each}}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- End My Project -->

    <!-- Script -->
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.8/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-I7E8VVD/ismYTF4hNIPjVp/Zjvgyol6VFvRkX/vR+Vc4jQkC+hVqc2pM8ODewa9r"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-BBtl+eGJRgqQAUMxJ7pMwbEyER4l1g+O15P+16Ep7Q9Q+zqX6gSbd85u4mG4QzX+"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    {{!-- <script src="js/index.js"></script> --}}
    <!-- End Script -->
  </body>
</html>